com.capgemini.cobigen.impl.model

Class ModelBuilderImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.capgemini.cobigen.impl.model.ModelBuilderImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ModelBuilder

    public class ModelBuilderImpl
extends Object
implements ModelBuilder
    The ModelBuilderImpl is responsible to create the object models for a given object. Therefore, it uses TriggerInterpreter plug-in extensions to query available InputReaders and MatcherInterpreters
